winter country
Homonym Number:
Word Class:noun
Sense Number: 1
Definition:land that is north-facing and at sufficiently low altitude for stock to safely graze during winter.
Origin:[none]
Register:
Register 2:
Flag: Farm Words
Domain:Rural
Region:[none]
See:safe country, wintering country
Pronunciation:
Notes:
